::Kluster::

Kluster reaches Phobia's ship, stopping. "Here you are. If you'd exuse me, I 
need to join the battle."

He runs toward the Cybertronian Fire, grinning as he passes the charred 
Mosquitor, an example of the raw power of his ship.
